data.description: This property is a true gem, boasting a myriad of desirable features that will undaoutbedly make you fall in love. Situated on a spacious corner lot, this residence offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and functionality. As you step inside, you'll immediately appreciate the open floor plan that creates a sense of spaciousness and connection throughout the home. Natural light floods the living spaces, thanks to all the windows and the inviting design. The large trees that adorn the property not only provide shade and privacy but also infuse a sense of tranquility and beauty. The private backyard is a retreat in itself, complete with a storage building for all your tools and outdoor equipment. The covered front and back porches allow you to relax and unwind, whether you're sipping your morning coffee or enjoying a barbecue with friends and family. The heart of this home is undoutbedly the large kitchen, equipped with an island that serves as the perfect gathering sport. Granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and an abundance of cabinets make the space both functional and aesthetically pleasing. The family room features a vaulted ceiling, giving the space an air of grandeur, and a fireplace that adds a cozy ambiance on chilly evenings. It's the ideal sport for entertaining guests or spending quality time with loved ones. The utility room offers added convenience, complete with a sink and cabinets for your laundry needs. The primary bath offers a double vanity, garden tub, and separate shower. Additionally, the formal dining area can easily be transformed into an office, providing a versatile space to meet your unique needs. This property showcases the perfect combination of indoor and outdoor living. You'll have the freedom to enjoy peaceful momentus, entertain, and work from home in a serene environment. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this fantastic property your very own.
